To Run the Code:

1) open teh project on VSCode or Ecllipse
2) run the ChatServer.java class first to start the server 
3) run the ChatClient.java to add a client to the Chat Room and exchange messages.

Note: 
to add a new client just run another instance of ChatClient class on the same port and each user can reply to the messages.
to start the conversation from start or make another chatroom just change the port in both the ChatServer.java and ChatClient.java classes.
